WEBVTT

01:38.320 --> 01:40.520
EPISODE 11

01:41.760 --> 01:42.880
There's an empty seat.

01:42.960 --> 01:44.280
Will you scoot over?

02:01.280 --> 02:03.440
- Banshan!
- Isn't that the department belle?

02:12.120 --> 02:13.800
FOURTH QUARTER
COMPUTER VS. ARCHITECTURE

02:14.000 --> 02:16.920
My goodness! Look! Isn't that Bei Weiwei?

02:17.120 --> 02:20.560
- The legendary campus belle runner-up?
- Yes!

02:22.080 --> 02:24.360
Why is Xiao Nai sitting
next to Bei Weiwei?

02:24.440 --> 02:25.480
Is that a coincidence?

02:25.560 --> 02:28.240
No way! I'm telling you!

02:28.320 --> 02:30.000
They must be dating!

02:30.760 --> 02:31.760
Just now,

02:31.840 --> 02:34.160
I saw Xiao Nai bringing her here
on his bike.

02:34.560 --> 02:38.200
Our idol Xiao Nai is nailed down
by Weiwei, just like that?

02:46.920 --> 02:48.720
Meng Yiran is here, too.

02:49.000 --> 02:51.240
Do you think she came to see Xiao Nai?

02:52.200 --> 02:54.400
Probably, but I think,

02:54.480 --> 02:56.200
since Bei Weiwei nailed Xiao Nai down,

02:56.280 --> 02:58.280
that's even more prestigious
than being the campus belle!

02:58.800 --> 03:00.600
Tell me something I don't know.

03:03.920 --> 03:07.160
It's all your fault!
Why did you drag me here?

03:09.600 --> 03:13.880
I didn't know, either!
Why don't we leave now?

03:14.480 --> 03:18.440
No, if we leave now,
what would people say of me?

03:32.880 --> 03:33.720
The score is tied.

03:34.920 --> 03:38.280
Don't worry. When they stop
looking up at the bleachers,

03:38.360 --> 03:39.360
the score gap will widen again.

03:53.720 --> 03:56.280
Why are we leading by only two points?

04:01.440 --> 04:04.280
I forgot to introduce them.
These are my roommates.

04:04.360 --> 04:07.360
Erxi, Xiaoling, and Sisi.

04:07.480 --> 04:08.880
Hi, nice to meet you.

04:14.880 --> 04:17.120
Comparison does show differences.

04:17.200 --> 04:18.279
Compared to them,

04:18.360 --> 04:21.440
my reaction to Lord is pretty good.

04:23.680 --> 04:26.040
Shoot from the baseline... Take the ball.

04:27.680 --> 04:29.640
Yugong and Houzi are down there.

04:29.720 --> 04:31.440
Do you want to go say hi?

04:35.520 --> 04:39.240
- Are they numbers 10 and 11?
- Yes.

04:42.200 --> 04:45.200
- What about Mo Zha Ta?
- He's not here.

04:49.360 --> 04:51.240
Do they know I'm Luwei Weiwei?

04:52.160 --> 04:53.120
No.

04:55.480 --> 04:56.440
I'll go.

05:04.560 --> 05:07.440
Wait for me. Let's head back together.

05:15.040 --> 05:17.800
Did Xiao Nai buy all those snacks?

05:19.000 --> 05:21.120
Who cares about the snacks now?

05:21.320 --> 05:25.440
The world is so fantastical! Erxi! Sisi!

05:25.920 --> 05:29.160
Weiwei and Xiao Nai are so compatible!
Who said otherwise?

05:29.240 --> 05:32.280
- People on the forum know nothing!
- Right?

05:34.680 --> 05:36.000
Nicely done!

05:40.200 --> 05:47.120
Has the forever-single guy finally
embraced social norms, Nai?

05:47.680 --> 05:49.920
Hi, I'm Weiwei. Nice to meet you guys.

05:50.520 --> 05:51.560
- Hello!
- Hi...

05:53.680 --> 05:56.520
I mean, I'm Luwei Weiwei.

05:59.560 --> 06:04.960
- What? What's going on, Nai?
- What do you think?

06:05.360 --> 06:09.080
- Darn it! That's fate!
- You're good, Xiao Nai!

06:09.160 --> 06:11.400
You nailed down our department belle!

06:11.640 --> 06:12.840
Do tell, who took the initiative?

06:13.200 --> 06:15.640
That's obvious! Look at Lord Xiao Nai!

06:15.720 --> 06:18.520
He went up to the bleachers
before the game was over.

06:18.600 --> 06:20.960
He has none of the airs
of a campus celebrity.

06:21.280 --> 06:23.920
I'm sure it's Xiao Nai
who went after Weiwei.

06:24.440 --> 06:25.960
Guessing is too much hassle.

06:26.040 --> 06:27.840
Girl, tell us who took the initiative!

06:27.920 --> 06:29.240
I want to hear your first-hand account.

06:29.920 --> 06:31.080
I know!

06:31.600 --> 06:34.080
They've long been eating
the forbidden brew.

06:35.040 --> 06:35.960
"The forbidden brew"?

06:36.240 --> 06:38.080
Why cough? You're worried I'd expose you?

06:39.040 --> 06:40.120
It's "eating the forbidden fruit."

06:42.720 --> 06:44.920
Also, don't use that phrase lightly.

06:47.320 --> 06:48.440
- Does it matter?
- No...

06:48.520 --> 06:50.640
- Does it matter?
- No...

06:50.720 --> 06:51.960
What matters now,

06:52.040 --> 06:54.240
is that you're a happy couple
and we won the game.

06:54.320 --> 06:55.520
Shouldn't it be your treat tonight?

06:55.600 --> 06:58.800
- Treat us to a meal...
- You're the best, Banshan. Treat...

06:58.880 --> 07:00.840
We're hungry after the game.

07:00.920 --> 07:04.080
- Let's get a late-night supper!
- Let's go...

07:04.160 --> 07:07.600
- Nai's treating, Mrs. Nai has to come!
- Don't scare her.

07:07.680 --> 07:09.440
I'll go, but she'll take a rain check.

07:09.520 --> 07:12.400
No way! You're half
of the lead cast today.

07:12.480 --> 07:15.480
- The main event is our department belle.
- Yes...

07:15.560 --> 07:17.120
- Why can't your girlfriend come with us?
- Fine!

07:17.200 --> 07:19.560
I won't interfere. You ask her.

07:19.960 --> 07:21.720
- Will you come with?
- Let's go eat!

07:21.800 --> 07:24.280
- Come on!
- Guys, I have to go.

07:24.360 --> 07:27.440
My roommates are waiting for me.
See you later!

07:30.040 --> 07:31.480
What time do you usually go study?

07:33.280 --> 07:37.000
- Half past seven.
- Okay, I'll wait downstairs tomorrow.

07:40.800 --> 07:45.920
- Weiwei, save me a seat.
- Okay.

07:54.040 --> 07:55.000
Let's go.

08:01.880 --> 08:03.920
- Come on, let's get changed.
- Okay.

08:04.000 --> 08:06.040
- Let's go.
- We'll go change.

08:06.120 --> 08:07.600
Bye-bye...

08:08.480 --> 08:09.880
Where is she?

08:09.960 --> 08:12.680
- Who?
- Nai's girlfriend.

08:14.880 --> 08:16.400
You're too late. She's gone.

08:17.520 --> 08:19.720
I came as soon as I got the news.

08:21.200 --> 08:24.760
Nai, ask her to come back.
I want to see her in person.

08:25.360 --> 08:26.840
You'll see her soon enough.

08:27.160 --> 08:29.800
Let's go. It's Yugong's treat tonight.

08:29.960 --> 08:32.559
Why me?
I don't have money or a girlfriend.

08:33.360 --> 08:36.159
I spent all my money
treating Weiwei to lunch.

08:39.480 --> 08:43.200
Crap... Nai's gotten the bad habit
of showing off his girlfriend.

08:43.280 --> 08:45.360
How will we live from now on?

09:03.680 --> 09:05.280
Ask away, if you want.

09:07.080 --> 09:09.480
Why didn't you tell us
you've been dating Xiao Nai?

09:09.560 --> 09:14.120
You've got it wrong!
I only just found out, too.

09:14.880 --> 09:16.480
Do you take us for fools?

09:16.560 --> 09:18.040
By the looks of you two today,

09:18.120 --> 09:21.240
no one would believe
you haven't been dating for half a year!

09:21.320 --> 09:23.800
Half a year? More like half an hour!

09:27.960 --> 09:30.560
I need ten uninterrupted minutes
to make a statement.

09:31.360 --> 09:34.440
- Quick! Tell us everything.
- Which base have you gotten to?

09:34.840 --> 09:37.800
Have you kissed? When was the first kiss?

09:41.080 --> 09:43.120
What happened was,

09:44.120 --> 09:46.160
a few months ago,

09:46.440 --> 09:51.920
it was a sunny, cloudless day,
when the moon was bright and stars few.

09:52.800 --> 09:56.680
I logged on to the game
and went to the bathroom...

09:56.760 --> 09:58.520
Get to the point!

09:59.600 --> 10:04.640
The point comes after I used the bathroom!
So impatient!

10:05.640 --> 10:07.600
When I came out of the bathroom,

10:07.680 --> 10:10.480
I was surrounded by a bunch of players,

10:10.560 --> 10:13.360
who thought I was there
to storm the wedding.

10:16.440 --> 10:18.760
Then we agreed to meet.

10:18.920 --> 10:22.400
That's when I realized
Yixiao Naihe is Xiao Nai.

10:24.080 --> 10:26.960
So you only met two hours ago?

10:27.440 --> 10:30.280
I didn't keep it from you.
You had it wrong.

10:30.360 --> 10:34.600
So you met Xiao Nai just now,
and he's got you nailed down?

10:36.360 --> 10:39.240
I guess so.

10:42.200 --> 10:46.160
If there's a next time,
I'll try to hold out until the next day.

10:46.240 --> 10:48.800
Forget it! There won't be a next time.

10:49.400 --> 10:52.640
I told you she's in love!

10:52.760 --> 10:57.120
But I never expected the guy to be
Lord Xiao Nai! It's so fantastical!

10:58.440 --> 11:03.440
Weiwei, does Lord know
you're his fangirl?

11:06.360 --> 11:10.720
Don't worry.
I'm his fangirl in the game, too.

11:10.800 --> 11:13.880
He won't feel weird in real life.

11:15.320 --> 11:18.640
You're really getting more...

11:19.160 --> 11:21.680
I don't even know how to describe you.

11:22.120 --> 11:24.440
By the way, you haven't shown us

11:24.520 --> 11:26.280
the video you made.

11:26.920 --> 11:28.280
I'll show you at the dorm.

11:32.800 --> 11:35.840
The video is the reason why
we met up today!

11:36.720 --> 11:38.640
I totally forgot about that.

11:40.520 --> 11:44.480
The combined power of Xiao Nai and Naihe
is too overwhelming.

11:48.560 --> 11:50.880
It's true, when in love,

11:50.960 --> 11:53.600
a person's IQ nosedives.

11:54.560 --> 11:56.880
Lord Xiao is incredible.

11:57.280 --> 12:00.200
Even his courtship is like a blitz.

12:08.680 --> 12:11.120
Was my three-pointer awesome or what?

12:12.400 --> 12:13.840
Forget it! What was that?

12:16.440 --> 12:19.400
- What's up, Girly?
- Shush...

12:20.400 --> 12:21.520
What is it?

12:21.600 --> 12:25.640
Somehow, I feel a little uneasy.

12:28.440 --> 12:30.320
Now Nai has a girl and you don't.

12:30.400 --> 12:33.880
- So you're particularly upset.
- You're jealous...

12:33.960 --> 12:37.280
No way! Why would I be jealous of Nai?

12:37.360 --> 12:39.120
A girl will come eventually.

12:39.200 --> 12:42.840
I'm just thinking about
the Mrs. Nai in the game.

12:45.240 --> 12:47.840
Just think, in real life,

12:47.920 --> 12:49.120
Nai has a girlfriend.

12:49.200 --> 12:51.520
As his buddies, we're happy for him.

12:52.200 --> 12:53.760
But come to think of it,

12:53.840 --> 12:55.920
what about the Mrs. Nai in the game?

12:56.320 --> 12:59.240
She just got stood up at the finals,

12:59.320 --> 13:01.840
and now Nai has a new girlfriend.

13:02.440 --> 13:05.480
I... I just feel so awful for her.

13:05.560 --> 13:07.800
Listen, your worry--

13:08.640 --> 13:11.600
- There's a mosquito.
- Houzi, tell me!

13:11.760 --> 13:13.280
Your worry is so right!

13:13.440 --> 13:15.240
- Right?
- Yeah.

13:15.760 --> 13:18.360
Yeah...

13:19.240 --> 13:20.760
Nai is a womanizer!

13:21.480 --> 13:23.520
A Mrs. Nai in the game.
A Mrs. Nai in real life.

13:23.600 --> 13:25.800
Mrs. Nai in the game must be heartbroken!

13:25.880 --> 13:27.280
Heartbroken!

13:27.360 --> 13:31.600
Right? No, today,

13:31.680 --> 13:33.800
I must stand up

13:33.880 --> 13:35.280
for the Mrs. Nai in the game.

13:35.800 --> 13:37.880
Will you go on behalf of us three?

13:37.960 --> 13:40.120
Good luck, bro. I believe in you.

13:40.200 --> 13:41.720
I... Believe in you, too.

13:52.800 --> 13:56.200
Nai, I need to talk to you.

13:58.040 --> 14:00.680
You've got a girlfriend in real life,

14:00.760 --> 14:02.360
the department belle, at that.

14:02.520 --> 14:04.680
As your buddy, I'm happy for you.

14:05.960 --> 14:10.000
But, have you thought about
the Mrs. Nai in the game?

14:10.720 --> 14:12.400
What about the Mrs. Nai in the game?

14:13.360 --> 14:16.800
Right... Nai, what about
the Mrs. Nai in the game?

14:16.880 --> 14:19.040
- Explain yourself.
- Give him an answer.

14:21.280 --> 14:22.400
Then I'll have to keep them both.

14:25.760 --> 14:28.080
Nai, are you... serious?

14:29.240 --> 14:30.160
I can't be more serious.

14:32.720 --> 14:35.600
Nai... You really are a womanizer!

14:37.480 --> 14:41.080
What's the hold-up? Hurry up!

14:41.160 --> 14:42.520
- Okay...
- Go, I'll catch up.

14:42.600 --> 14:43.920
We'll catch up.

14:44.360 --> 14:47.320
Why are you two laughing?
Did I say something wrong?

14:47.880 --> 14:50.920
No, not at all.

14:51.080 --> 14:53.600
- Nai!
- 100 percent, original...

14:53.680 --> 14:55.520
- Pure womanizer.
- No additives.

14:58.240 --> 15:01.520
- What's going on?
- Ask Weiwei.

15:06.320 --> 15:12.200
Weiwei? The department belle
is named Bei Weiwei.

15:12.480 --> 15:15.960
The Mrs. Nai in the game is called
Luwei Weiwei.

15:17.480 --> 15:20.000
They're not the same person, are they?

15:20.280 --> 15:22.760
- They're the same person.
- One and the same.

15:23.760 --> 15:26.720
Yugong! Houzi! You guys...

15:26.800 --> 15:27.880
Let's go!

15:28.520 --> 15:30.680
I'll get you! Come back here!

15:33.840 --> 15:35.000
The booze is here...

15:35.080 --> 15:36.000
Hurry...

15:36.080 --> 15:37.800
- What took you so long?
- Hurry...

15:37.880 --> 15:39.760
I've always known Nai to be efficient,

15:39.840 --> 15:41.880
but I had no idea how efficient!

15:41.960 --> 15:43.920
He nailed down the department belle

15:44.000 --> 15:45.560
in the blink of an eye.

15:45.840 --> 15:48.160
Xiao Nai, how did you win over
our department belle?

15:48.240 --> 15:50.960
Give us some pointers.
We're about to graduate,

15:51.040 --> 15:53.440
a bunch of us are still lonely
and single.

15:53.520 --> 15:54.880
Doesn't it pain you to see us like this?

15:55.240 --> 15:57.560
This is a gift.

15:59.360 --> 16:02.240
- I finally realized something.
- What?

16:02.640 --> 16:04.320
Nai and I ran into the department belle

16:04.920 --> 16:06.440
on a few occasions.

16:07.120 --> 16:09.760
I said, "Don't you think
fate has brought us together?"

16:10.400 --> 16:12.520
- You know what he said?
- What?

16:12.920 --> 16:15.920
He said, "Even if that's true,

16:16.200 --> 16:17.040
what's that got to do with you?"

16:17.400 --> 16:20.160
Somebody was jealous!

16:20.240 --> 16:21.240
Here, let's drink!

16:21.320 --> 16:23.880
- Let's drink...
- Drink...

16:27.880 --> 16:29.120
I must say, though,

16:29.200 --> 16:31.800
Xiao Nai did this brilliantly.

16:31.960 --> 16:33.840
Our computer department

16:33.920 --> 16:35.880
finally had a campus belle runner-up,

16:35.960 --> 16:38.040
and she's not dating
outside the department!

16:38.400 --> 16:40.320
If she got snatched up
by another department,

16:40.400 --> 16:43.120
how will that reflect on us? Right?

16:43.200 --> 16:45.600
Hey... What "campus belle runner-up"?

16:45.680 --> 16:47.000
Don't you know any better?

16:48.320 --> 16:51.880
Mrs. Nai is a master both pen and sword.
She's definitely number one!

16:51.960 --> 16:53.600
The ranking is nonsense.

16:54.880 --> 16:56.880
- I'll drink to it.
- Drink to it.

16:58.040 --> 17:00.840
Wasn't there a bit of controversy
over the contest?

17:01.800 --> 17:04.599
It was Meng Yiran versus Nai's girl.

17:04.800 --> 17:06.839
How come Nai's girl lost?

17:07.119 --> 17:10.839
I know what happened.
My girlfriend is Mrs. Nai's roommate.

17:11.240 --> 17:12.520
According to her,

17:12.599 --> 17:15.680
someone covertly snapped a photo
of Mrs. Nail, so it was blurry.

17:16.000 --> 17:18.079
It didn't do her justice at all.

17:18.160 --> 17:19.319
There was another key factor.

17:19.760 --> 17:23.920
They said she lost, because she's not
as innocent-looking as Meng.

17:25.119 --> 17:26.040
What ranking?

17:26.880 --> 17:28.319
Seriously, Nai?

17:28.920 --> 17:32.120
You don't know our department
has a beauty ranking?

17:32.200 --> 17:33.920
But you should know this one:

17:34.680 --> 17:36.320
risk index list.

17:37.240 --> 17:40.240
Mrs. Nai is number one.

17:44.720 --> 17:45.560
Let me borrow your laptop.

17:45.840 --> 17:48.360
What's going on? You need the laptop now?

17:53.640 --> 17:54.560
Come on... Let's drink.

17:54.960 --> 17:57.280
- Here...
- Let's drink...

18:03.760 --> 18:05.160
What's Xiao Nai doing?

18:05.720 --> 18:08.240
Is he voting for girls?

18:10.200 --> 18:11.040
Let me see.

18:21.600 --> 18:24.760
What have you done, Nai?

18:25.320 --> 18:28.720
Why keep rankings
that are based on seriously flawed data?

18:37.280 --> 18:38.480
You're unbelievable.

18:40.080 --> 18:42.880
Here's to Nai and Mrs. Nai.

18:43.440 --> 18:45.480
- Cheers!
- Cheers...

18:45.560 --> 18:47.440
Here's to us escaping singlehood soon!

18:47.520 --> 18:49.600
- Escape singlehood... It's a must!
- Hear, hear!

18:49.680 --> 18:50.840
Cheers...

18:50.960 --> 18:52.520
The school's forum has exploded

18:52.600 --> 18:54.280
over Nai and Bei Weiwei.

18:54.360 --> 18:55.560
- Exploded?
- It exploded?

18:55.640 --> 18:57.120
Looks like it.

18:58.160 --> 18:59.880
- It's exploded, Nai!
- Nai, it's exploded!

18:59.960 --> 19:01.480
- It has!
- It's true.

19:02.480 --> 19:05.320
Lord Xiao Nai? Why is he with her?

19:05.400 --> 19:08.160
- I don't believe it.
- How did they get together?

19:37.680 --> 19:38.840
Hello, Sir.

19:39.280 --> 19:42.000
This is the best-selling item
of our brand.

19:42.200 --> 19:44.200
Is this for your girlfriend?

19:45.160 --> 19:46.400
Yes.

19:46.560 --> 19:49.400
- Can I see it?
- Sure. Just a second.

19:51.080 --> 19:52.040
Here you go.

19:55.520 --> 19:57.040
It's a very expensive gift.

19:57.120 --> 19:59.400
Your girlfriend will be thrilled.

20:07.560 --> 20:08.520
Cao Guang!

20:09.240 --> 20:11.360
You're going out so late, Dali?

20:11.440 --> 20:13.040
Where have you been?
Why didn't you answer my call?

20:13.120 --> 20:14.640
My phone's dead.

20:16.240 --> 20:18.480
You went gift-shopping? For whom?

20:20.160 --> 20:22.640
You know who it's for. Why ask?

20:22.720 --> 20:24.480
It's all thanks to your idea.

20:25.200 --> 20:28.080
Playing to the girl's interest
is a great tactic!

20:28.160 --> 20:31.000
The world of gaming is indeed different.

20:31.120 --> 20:35.000
Didn't you see the school forum,
Cao Guang?

20:35.760 --> 20:40.000
- Right, your phone's dead.
- School forum? What's up?

20:44.560 --> 20:45.720
Read it yourself.

20:46.160 --> 20:47.560
What?

20:52.040 --> 20:54.360
- What's this?
- What else?

20:54.440 --> 20:56.840
Bei Weiwei is with Xiao Nai.

20:58.880 --> 21:01.320
Everyone saw it.
It's all over the school forum.

21:01.400 --> 21:02.240
That's impossible!

21:03.400 --> 21:06.280
Photos don't lie.
These aren't photoshopped.

21:15.880 --> 21:19.480
- Where are you going, Cao Guang?
- Basketball gym.

21:19.560 --> 21:22.520
You... What are you thinking?

21:22.600 --> 21:25.440
Look at the time! The game ended long ago.

21:47.280 --> 21:50.200
Don't be upset, Yiran.

21:50.520 --> 21:53.640
Maybe they're not really dating.

21:54.760 --> 21:57.680
Even if they are,
Xiao Nai obviously isn't thinking right.

21:58.320 --> 22:01.440
Girls like Bei Weiwei
are so manipulative.

22:03.920 --> 22:07.080
It's all your fault!
Why did you drag me to the game?

22:07.480 --> 22:08.320
I...

22:09.200 --> 22:11.960
I had no idea that would happen.

22:12.480 --> 22:13.800
I only did it for your sake.

22:15.120 --> 22:16.360
For my sake?

22:16.440 --> 22:18.400
You're always egging me on,
to do this and that.

22:18.480 --> 22:21.280
And then? Nothing has worked!

22:21.360 --> 22:24.640
Meanwhile, the entire school
knows Xiao Nai...

22:25.440 --> 22:27.480
Xiao Nai is with Bei Weiwei.

22:28.280 --> 22:30.040
Why did I go to the game?

22:30.120 --> 22:31.600
What do people think of me?

22:33.520 --> 22:38.920
Yiran, they don't necessarily know
you like Xiao Nai.

22:42.040 --> 22:43.200
Look at it!

22:45.400 --> 22:47.520
Is this Bei Weiwei's counterattack
against Meng Yiran?

22:47.600 --> 22:49.000
I voted for Bei Weiwei.

22:49.320 --> 22:51.440
Why do I somehow feel thrilled?

22:51.720 --> 22:54.440
I've heard the campus belle was courting
Lord Xiao Nai.

22:54.640 --> 22:56.200
Now he got intercepted by Bei Weiwei!

22:56.280 --> 22:58.960
The campus belle must be
crying her eyes out now.

23:03.480 --> 23:05.000
Tell me, what do we do now?

23:06.920 --> 23:10.080
Calm down, Yiran.

23:10.760 --> 23:12.360
Why don't you go home and rest?

23:12.800 --> 23:14.720
Didn't you ask me to pick up
some things for you?

23:14.800 --> 23:15.760
I haven't gone to the store.

23:15.840 --> 23:17.400
Why don't I go right now?

23:17.480 --> 23:20.120
I'll also get your favorite orange juice.

23:20.880 --> 23:22.440
That'll cheer you up, no?

23:34.560 --> 23:36.440
Why take it out on me?

23:36.880 --> 23:39.080
Is it my fault Xiao Nai ignores you?

23:39.520 --> 23:42.000
You can't net him,
yet you take it out on me?

23:43.720 --> 23:47.160
Who do you think you are?
A prima donna is what you are!

23:47.480 --> 23:50.440
You think you can boss me around,
for treating me to Japanese twice?

23:50.520 --> 23:55.360
If it weren't for...
I'd never wait on you!

23:58.240 --> 24:00.880
Slow down! It's just the two of us.
There's plenty of booze...

24:03.360 --> 24:05.880
Are you trying to drown out your feelings?

24:06.480 --> 24:08.720
Is Bei Weiwei really worth it?

24:10.720 --> 24:13.920
Who hasn't had his heart broken?
You'll get used to it soon.

24:14.120 --> 24:16.160
Listen to me, stop drinking.

24:16.240 --> 24:17.920
A woman like that isn't worth it.

24:24.360 --> 24:25.880
Who told you my heart's broken?

24:25.960 --> 24:28.720
I'm just ashamed for having poor judgment.

24:29.800 --> 24:31.520
I always thought I was smart,

24:31.600 --> 24:35.080
yet I still failed to see
what a hussy Bei Weiwei is.

24:36.240 --> 24:37.760
Waiter! Two more bottles!

24:42.400 --> 24:45.480
Bud, I feel your pain.

24:46.360 --> 24:49.080
The thing is, I've always thought,

24:49.160 --> 24:51.800
beautiful girls like Bei Weiwei

24:51.880 --> 24:53.640
are mostly arrogant.

24:53.760 --> 24:57.240
When it comes to love,
they're always picky and snooty.

24:57.640 --> 24:59.680
I didn't want to say anything,

24:59.760 --> 25:01.040
since you were so keen on her.

25:02.640 --> 25:06.440
Now that things are what they are,
I can be frank with you.

25:07.120 --> 25:10.000
Maybe you're lucky
to not have anything to do with her.

25:11.600 --> 25:12.440
You think so, too?

25:16.040 --> 25:18.320
We're already a couple in the game,

25:18.400 --> 25:20.840
yet she's dating Xiao Nai in real life.

25:20.920 --> 25:22.400
Does she think it's a game,
so it doesn't count?

25:22.480 --> 25:24.680
Does she think it's a game,
so she can toy with someone's heart?

25:28.840 --> 25:30.240
I've been blind to the truth!

25:30.840 --> 25:34.200
I thought, despite her looks,
she was still kindhearted.

25:35.240 --> 25:38.440
I didn't know she's remarkably consistent.

25:41.720 --> 25:43.120
Let the past rest.

25:43.920 --> 25:45.400
A guy like you can have the pick

25:45.480 --> 25:48.520
of any of those pretty and innocent girls

25:48.600 --> 25:50.040
of the Foreign Languages Department.

25:50.720 --> 25:52.120
Who cares for

25:52.200 --> 25:55.400
those high-IQ, low-EQ
science and engineering girls?

25:59.440 --> 26:01.320
I underestimated her.

26:02.680 --> 26:06.200
She's such as good actress.
How could she have low EQ?

26:06.480 --> 26:12.000
True, she's totally into you in the game,

26:12.360 --> 26:15.880
yet in real life, she's sweet on Xiao Nai.

26:16.960 --> 26:20.200
She deserves an Oscar
for best leading actress, no?

26:23.240 --> 26:25.760
All right... What's Bei Weiwei anyway?

26:26.080 --> 26:28.880
Get a good night's sleep,
and break up with her tomorrow.

26:30.600 --> 26:32.120
- Break up?
- Yes.

26:33.800 --> 26:35.040
Why break up?

26:35.640 --> 26:37.520
She can act, but so can I.

26:38.040 --> 26:40.000
I'll start acting tomorrow, too.

26:41.600 --> 26:44.120
Just you wait, Bei Weiwei!

26:53.320 --> 26:55.080
- Hey, we're taking off.
- See you.

26:55.160 --> 26:56.760
Bye-bye...

26:56.840 --> 26:58.400
- Taking off...
- See you tomorrow.

26:58.480 --> 26:59.360
Goodbye.

27:10.360 --> 27:11.360
Nai,

27:12.760 --> 27:14.520
thanks for risking your life to save me.
Cheers!

27:17.680 --> 27:21.280
I did save you, but I didn't risk my life.

27:22.080 --> 27:25.200
If you weren't in the way,
I'm confident we could've dodged it.

27:25.840 --> 27:28.280
Nai, you were that confident?

27:29.400 --> 27:31.160
In that split second, yes.

27:31.360 --> 27:33.240
Plus, the vehicle itself was safe enough.

27:33.680 --> 27:35.160
What about the unexpected factors?

27:35.440 --> 27:38.760
Even so, it'd still minimize the harm.

27:40.520 --> 27:42.200
Here's to you, Nai.

27:43.160 --> 27:44.400
Put it down.

27:45.560 --> 27:47.520
You gave it all on the court today.

27:47.600 --> 27:48.680
We're all super touched.

27:49.240 --> 27:51.960
You just recovered from your injuries.
Don't drink.

27:53.480 --> 27:55.640
You're saying that,
after I've been drinking all night?

27:56.080 --> 27:58.680
This is only 3.8 percent alcohol.
It's nothing.

28:04.400 --> 28:05.560
I need to use the toilet.

28:09.680 --> 28:12.600
He told us to keep it a secret,
to avoid being embarrassed,

28:12.680 --> 28:14.320
but he told you anyway.

28:15.840 --> 28:17.040
A bit of booze and he lets it all out.

28:17.480 --> 28:20.000
He just might regret it tomorrow.

28:20.600 --> 28:23.720
Anyway, you guys go ahead.
I need to use the bathroom, too.

28:25.680 --> 28:29.240
Those two can't hold their liquor.
Cheers.

28:51.640 --> 28:52.640
It is you!

28:53.680 --> 28:55.800
Aren't you our cafeteria's lunch dude...

28:57.320 --> 28:59.240
No, I mean,

28:59.320 --> 29:03.560
one of our cafeteria staff.

29:04.880 --> 29:06.040
Sorry.

29:06.720 --> 29:07.760
It's okay.

29:08.520 --> 29:10.720
You don't work at the cafeteria anymore?

29:11.920 --> 29:12.920
I work here at night.

29:14.880 --> 29:16.800
Your food is particularly yummy.

29:17.080 --> 29:19.920
Earlier, I thought
the food tonight tasted familiar.

29:20.400 --> 29:23.080
I've been going to your cafeteria
every day since.

29:23.880 --> 29:24.960
I know.

29:25.360 --> 29:30.480
You do? Do you know me?

29:36.920 --> 29:38.400
Well, I'll let you get back to work.

29:39.400 --> 29:43.400
By the way, the veggies at school
are underseasoned.

29:43.480 --> 29:45.560
Can you add a bit more salt?

29:46.640 --> 29:48.320
I don't cook all the dishes at school.

29:49.440 --> 29:51.960
No wonder, some dishes are gorgeous,

29:52.040 --> 29:53.680
while others are hideous.

30:01.800 --> 30:04.400
What's that? Names of dishes?

30:08.720 --> 30:12.160
I'm in charge of making these dishes.
You can order them.

30:14.400 --> 30:16.160
Why don't we exchange numbers?

30:18.520 --> 30:21.520
I'm just a cook, kitchen staff.

30:25.280 --> 30:28.640
I'm just a programmer, a coder.

30:49.720 --> 30:51.480
Still can't sleep.

30:53.280 --> 30:54.200
Misread?

30:55.200 --> 30:57.400
They'd think we're...

30:58.320 --> 30:59.200
In that kind of a relationship.

31:00.080 --> 31:02.200
Since when aren't we in that kind
of a relationship?

31:10.040 --> 31:12.680
- Are you still up?
- I need the toilet.

31:21.120 --> 31:22.480
I must sleep,

31:22.720 --> 31:25.080
otherwise I'll have dark circles
under my eyes tomorrow.

31:25.160 --> 31:26.680
That'd be bad.

31:43.480 --> 31:45.040
Weiwei!

31:46.440 --> 31:47.680
Weiwei!

31:49.680 --> 31:50.760
What's the matter?

31:50.840 --> 31:55.800
- I had the runs three times. I'm dying.
- What's wrong?

31:56.160 --> 31:58.320
Erxi seems to have really bad diarrhea.

31:59.280 --> 32:01.640
Take her to the campus doctor.

32:01.720 --> 32:04.800
But the campus doctors are notorious.

32:05.800 --> 32:07.280
Take her to the hospital.

32:07.680 --> 32:10.400
Call a cab and have them wait
by the gates.

32:10.480 --> 32:12.040
I'll get you some hot water.

32:12.360 --> 32:14.200
What else do you need to bring?

32:14.280 --> 32:15.360
Lay down.

32:27.320 --> 32:30.480
Did I eat something bad?

32:30.720 --> 32:33.200
How did this happen so suddenly?

32:34.480 --> 32:37.280
You can get dehydrated
from acute gastroenteritis.

32:37.360 --> 32:40.040
I'll get some hot water.
You should keep drinking it.

32:41.360 --> 32:44.040
- Here we are. Be careful.
- Easy...

32:52.960 --> 32:54.320
Here, be careful.

33:12.760 --> 33:14.600
You should go back.

33:14.680 --> 33:18.760
The doctor said it's nothing serious.
I'll be fine after some sleep.

33:20.000 --> 33:22.480
Forget it. We're hoping,

33:22.560 --> 33:24.840
if we ever have diarrhea
or acute gastroenteritis,

33:24.920 --> 33:26.320
you'll take care of us.

33:26.400 --> 33:28.280
We're not doing this for free.
You owe us now.

33:30.760 --> 33:34.920
You guys are so nice. Our dorm is so nice.

33:37.360 --> 33:39.040
That's a fact. Lie down.

33:44.800 --> 33:46.640
Close your eyes and sleep.

34:22.679 --> 34:24.440
You're awake? Do you feel better?

34:26.120 --> 34:31.719
Weiwei, Lord bought
the snacks yesterday, right?

34:33.960 --> 34:34.960
Yes.

34:37.280 --> 34:40.600
I shouldn't have touched
the nobility's food.

34:41.120 --> 34:44.520
It's not something
my commoner's stomach can handle.

34:45.120 --> 34:48.280
Yeah, right! We all ate it.
Why are we perfectly fine?

34:49.159 --> 34:51.080
Don't blame everything on him.

34:51.520 --> 34:52.760
Tell me, honestly,

34:52.840 --> 34:55.440
did you secretly drink
too much of Sisi's diet tea?

35:09.760 --> 35:14.720
Weiwei, you're so pretty.
No wonder you can nail Lord down.

35:15.120 --> 35:19.040
What? It's my winning inner beauty, okay?

35:21.760 --> 35:23.240
Inner beauty?

35:28.960 --> 35:32.160
It's seven. I have to tell Lord
not to wait for me.

35:32.440 --> 35:33.480
Let me borrow your phone.

35:56.280 --> 35:59.640
First day dating, and I got exposed
for being a narcissist.

36:00.120 --> 36:02.120
Even though I was only kidding...

36:02.440 --> 36:04.800
What now? I urgently need a solution!

36:12.560 --> 36:14.960
Why did Lord show up?

36:16.000 --> 36:19.240
I called Dazhong this morning,
when I got up to use the toilet.

36:19.320 --> 36:22.080
He ran into Lord on the stairs,

36:22.600 --> 36:24.720
and he told him what happened.

36:24.880 --> 36:26.640
So he said, he'd come pick us up.

36:27.240 --> 36:29.800
Why didn't you tell us first?

36:29.880 --> 36:31.960
I haven't gotten a chance
to brush my teeth!

36:32.440 --> 36:36.280
It was only six o'clock.
You were all still asleep.

36:36.840 --> 36:40.600
Anyway, who cares
if you have brushed your teeth?

36:43.800 --> 36:45.760
I haven't brushed my teeth, either.

36:47.680 --> 36:51.680
I don't think it's appropriate
for Lord to pick us up.

36:51.760 --> 36:55.040
Why not? He's family now.

36:56.880 --> 37:00.280
"Family"?
Aren't you a bit presumptuous, Sisi?

37:00.360 --> 37:04.760
But it's Lord's car, we're commoners...

37:04.840 --> 37:07.080
Sisi is right, he's family...

37:15.640 --> 37:18.680
You haven't had breakfast, right?
Let's get some food.

37:20.800 --> 37:23.680
Lord is so sweet.
He rescued me from that awkward moment.

37:27.560 --> 37:30.240
It's okay.
You've already been a great help.

37:32.160 --> 37:34.280
We're family now. Don't worry.

37:36.720 --> 37:40.880
I knew it.
That sweet feeling was just an illusion.

37:54.360 --> 37:55.520
Easy...

38:01.920 --> 38:04.040
Thank you for the breakfast.

38:04.360 --> 38:06.680
Weiwei, we'll take Erxi upstairs now.

38:06.760 --> 38:08.560
Thank Mr. Xiao for us.

38:08.640 --> 38:09.800
For a minimum of three minutes.

38:10.680 --> 38:11.960
Bye-bye...

38:18.760 --> 38:19.840
Do you need to prepare?

38:21.640 --> 38:22.680
Prepare for what?

38:23.240 --> 38:25.840
Three minutes, right?
Your time starts now.

38:26.920 --> 38:29.280
They were joking.
Did you take it seriously?

38:29.560 --> 38:32.640
I might have accidentally
taken it seriously.

38:36.160 --> 38:38.240
I should go, too. Bye-bye.

39:20.960 --> 39:22.440
It smells so good.

39:22.520 --> 39:26.240
You're up? Food is really powerful.

39:26.320 --> 39:29.360
It wakes people effortlessly.
Come eat.

39:30.480 --> 39:33.120
- Come eat, Erxi.
- Wait...

39:34.440 --> 39:37.240
Are you all better?
You have energy to shop?

39:37.720 --> 39:40.360
Several big brands have
a seventy-percent-off online sale today.

39:40.440 --> 39:42.080
It starts at ten o'clock sharp.

39:42.160 --> 39:44.080
My well-being is the least of my concerns.

39:44.160 --> 39:46.000
If I miss out, I'll be more upset.

39:46.080 --> 39:49.040
Even cockroaches don't recover
at your pace.

39:49.640 --> 39:53.200
Yes, I'm a cockroach. So what?
What do you know?

39:53.280 --> 39:56.640
Sales are the only
potent remedy I need.

39:58.840 --> 40:01.080
By the way, Weiwei, come take a look.

40:02.040 --> 40:03.680
There are so many posts

40:03.760 --> 40:06.440
about you and Xiao Nai
on the school forum.

40:06.520 --> 40:10.720
There are pictures of you two
holding hands at the basketball gym, too.

40:13.640 --> 40:14.640
Let me see.

40:15.840 --> 40:19.480
Look! A lot of people
are incredulous at first.

40:19.560 --> 40:22.480
When the pictures were posted,
they were floored.

40:22.560 --> 40:23.800
Everyone's gossiping,

40:23.880 --> 40:25.920
wondering when you started dating.

40:27.640 --> 40:31.000
I thought the campus belle contest post
would be at the very top.

40:31.080 --> 40:32.520
How come it's not here?

40:33.400 --> 40:36.640
Our fellow students are too gossipy,
including you.

40:36.840 --> 40:40.040
It's exam time. The more exams,
the more gossipy they get.

40:40.120 --> 40:42.520
It's so-called pressure relief.

40:43.200 --> 40:46.200
It's ten! I better start shopping.

40:46.280 --> 40:48.880
Come give me your opinion on this dress.

40:50.280 --> 40:52.480
Hurry... Otherwise I won't get it!

40:52.920 --> 40:54.280
- This one.
- So annoying.

40:54.360 --> 40:56.520
It's good, and it's pretty cheap.

40:57.960 --> 40:59.000
This one?

41:02.160 --> 41:03.000
Hello?

41:04.120 --> 41:07.640
- You're up?
- Yes, I'm up.

41:07.720 --> 41:11.120
- Are you going to study later?
- Yes.

41:12.000 --> 41:14.840
But I don't think
I'll be able to find a spot now.

41:15.560 --> 41:18.200
There's a quiet place I can take you to.

41:37.800 --> 41:40.280
- Where are we going?
- You'll find out soon.

42:20.600 --> 42:21.800
The photos are online now.

42:21.880 --> 42:24.120
I guess I don't have to worry
about being seen?

42:25.280 --> 42:26.960
Aren't we going to the library?

42:27.480 --> 42:29.480
This place is off-campus.

45:02.960 --> 45:05.400
Subtitle translation by Lu Yuhan
